window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>How far would you go to save a friend?</p> <p>Nick Summerland traded in the hectic pace of Seattle for the familiar haunts of his hometown, Silvervale. He thought the move would dampen his curse: the ability to see life ticking away from those with less than a year to live.</p> <p>Instead of relief, he discovers one of the cursed death clocks hanging over his best friend.</p> <p>Nick learns Silvervale has its own secrets, including a beautiful, magic-wielding Medium who sees the same things he does, and a portal to an all-women’s college known as the Ghost Academy that might have the answers Nick needs.</p> <p>Still, all magic comes with a price, and saving his friend’s life won’t come easily. Nick must team up with female ghosts to hone his newfound abilities—all while holding down a 9 to 5 and navigating a budding relationship.</p> <p>As he’ll come to learn, not all ghosts are friendly—and some fates are worse than death.</p>"; 
